Disadvantages:

* Isolation:Ap community or ghr walon se dur hujate ho , zyada time akele mein apne computer ke saath guzaar rahay hutay ho,toh kaafi chhezain miss hujati hai ,kindly khayal rkhein.
* Variable Workload And Income: Fluctuate krti hai apki income stable nahi rehti ek jagah.
* Lack Of Job Security: Duniya mein ek hi cheez hai jo na hai pakki naukri pakki skillset.
* Growth Dillema: Growth dillema like ek hijagah nahi thike raho aagay badho or nayi cheezain seekho apni auqaat or badhao takay pese zyada kama sako.
* Social Circle: Din rt kaam krne social circle weak hujayega 
* Family Life: Social circle wala point yahan pr bhi fit bethega.
* Mental Health: Chirchirapan (lack of sleep ki wajah se), workload ki wjaah se , toh kya namaz mein dhayan de payein gaye , communication krpayein gaye ,mental health ka khayal rkhein